  {
    question: "Do you clean homes in Ross Bridge and Greystone golf communities?",
    answer: "Absolutely! We regularly clean homes in Ross Bridge, Greystone, and other Hoover golf communities. We're familiar with gate access procedures, HOA guidelines, and the larger floor plans typical of these master-planned communities. Many of our Ross Bridge and Greystone clients have recurring weekly or bi-weekly service to keep their beautiful homes in pristine condition year-round."
  },
  {
    question: "Are your cleaning products safe for families with children and pets?",
